text: In San Diego, it is on at 7:30. In the 7-8pm block, [Jeopardy or Wheel of Fortune starts first based on where in the country you are.](https://www.graphgraph.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/jeopardywheel_firstmarket_geo_graphgraph.png)
